title: Hard West Collector's Edition-GOG
description:
Hard West Collector's Edition (c) Gambitious Digital Entertainment

Release Date : 11/2015
Protection : -
Discs : 1
Genre : Adventure
Languages : EN/FR/DE/PL/RU

Welcome to the Wild West like youve never seen it before. When a
tragic turn of events sets one man down a path of supernatural
chaos and revenge, he must brutally hunt down all those whom
wronged him. Follow Warren on his descent into the darkest recesses
of the human soul, and try to survive in a world full of hard
choices and even harder consequences.

For more info go to : http://www.gog.com/game/hard_west
